data.description: Desirable single-story townhouse in Verona Trace. Built by Lennar in 2020, this 3 bed/2 bath/1 car garage home has a terrific open, split floor plan. Main bedroom has an en-suite bathroom with double sinks and walk in shower. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops and a pantry. Convenient separate laundry room with closet.  Home  has easy to use accordion shutters and an ADP alarm system installed. Enjoy all the amenities this community has to offer including pool, clubhouse, fitness center, tennis, basketball, playground and more! Close to I95 for commuters, lots of shopping, restaurants and the beach!
